{"tid":671623,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"附近有噪音問題 報左警都冇人理可以點","createTime":"2018-05-20T09:47:11.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-20T11:20:18.000Z","uid":158766,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"a3f60926b135067f57fc8d55d96641b59cf26175","tid":671623,"uid":158766,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-20T09:47:11.000Z","msg":"是咁的<br />\n<br />\n星期日公眾假期屋企樓下有個球場畀班疑似建制原居民團體book左 大概由下晝3點開始 班人除左開大喇叭揸住枝咪9叫「自私的中國人」呢類歌曲之外 仲請黎一堆大媽歌舞表演<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n但個球場離民居就唔夠30米 發出嘅聲浪極其滋擾 更慘嘅係報警後一個鐘仍未有警察到場了解或處理 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n而且早有另一團體係上兩個星期日於同一地點搞過活動 真係極其滋擾 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n次次一嘈我就好多野都做唔到 星期日自修室又只開到5點 我想走都冇咩地方可以去 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n請問各位ching有咩辦法對付呢類情況? 既然差佬唔肯做野 咁影下相拍下片交比傳媒煲大佢可唔可行？希望大家可以幫幫手 因為呢班自私喱真係好討厭呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"43c6f21481060cf39dec9efc6c4758d64013aee8","tid":671623,"uid":13739,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-20T09:49:15.000Z","msg":"用1823 app啦⋯⋯有效率到唔信"},{"pid":"bed5b07d7a77ce05ec794c3884fcbc9427a08793","tid":671623,"uid":179274,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-20T09:52:30.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"c1eab527e8aa3e15306178dc2d06e16eb4161a53","tid":671623,"uid":158766,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"43c6f21481060cf39dec9efc6c4758d64013aee8","tid":671623,"uid":13739,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-20T09:49:15.000Z","msg":"用1823 app啦⋯⋯有效率到